titleNullable: Wireless Corp Retail Business Data Authentic
subtitleNullable: T-Mobile,Ultra-Mobile,Business Analytics, Real Data, Original, Data Science
descriptionNullable:
Retail business data is considered hard to acquire and mysterious. To demystify the wireless service industry and provide business insights for general public, I created this dataset which was complied based on real world business transaction data, supplier data and other data in wireless service industry. 

The dataset describes a top-performing local wireless company's business transaction details during a 4 month period. You can expect to learn about potential costs, net earnings, product coverage and think about the business model in the wireless service industry.

Dataset has been preprocessed to include useful features like item, service category, supplier, profit contribution ratio, KPI benchmark, agent performance, etc.

Recommended data science tasks: Sales Dashboard Visualization, Classification, Regression,etc

The dataset was disclosed based on my consulting client's permission. All information guaranteed to be original.
